hands_on_practices.solution:
我们从 Bogoliubov 谱和密度涨落算符开始。

1. Bogoliubov 色散关系
$$\epsilon_{\mathbf q}=\frac{\hbar^2q^2}{2m},\qquad 
E_{\mathbf q}=\sqrt{\epsilon_{\mathbf q}\bigl(\epsilon_{\mathbf q}+2gn_0\bigr)}\,. $$

2. 静态结构因子
$$S(\mathbf q)
=\frac{1}{Vn_0}\langle\delta n(\mathbf q)\,\delta n(-\mathbf q)\rangle
=(u_{\mathbf q}-v_{\mathbf q})^2
=\frac{\epsilon_{\mathbf q}}{E_{\mathbf q}}\,. $$

3. 代入 $g=\frac{4\pi\hbar^2a_s}{m}$ 并化简：
$$\frac{\epsilon_{\mathbf q}}{E_{\mathbf q}}
=\frac{\frac{\hbar^2q^2}{2m}}
{\sqrt{\frac{\hbar^2q^2}{2m}\Bigl(\frac{\hbar^2q^2}{2m}+2g n_0\Bigr)}}
=\sqrt{\frac{\epsilon_{\mathbf q}}{\epsilon_{\mathbf q}+2g n_0}}
=\sqrt{\frac{\frac{\hbar^2q^2}{2m}}
{\frac{\hbar^2q^2}{2m}+2\frac{4\pi\hbar^2a_s}{m}n_0}}
=\sqrt{\frac{q^2}{\,q^2+16\pi a_s n_0\,}}\,. $$
